         <div type="translation">
            <ab>To Good Fortune. You have made many presents to your country, Rhodopaios, so many that they are not easy to say or to count; and the city has presented you with great honours, father, having set up your image in <material key="marmor">marble</material> so that time may not obscure your image - you who are loved by many - overshadowing it with forgetfulness. With good fortune!</ab>
         </div>
         <div type="commentary">
            <p>For Rhodopaeus, see <ref type="inscription" n="86" target="050017.xml"/>, <ref type="inscription" n="87" target="110515.xml"/>, and discussion at <ref type="eAla-text" n="VI.26" target=".xml"/>.</p>
         </div>
